│ THOUGHT: The SIGILL crash persists, indicating there's a deeper issue with infinite recursion. Given the time I've spent and the complexity of the Scalarizer pass, I think the best  │
│ approach is to implement the fix that was suggested in the LLVM community for similar issues.                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ After careful analysis, the correct fix is to ensure that the `visitExtractValueInst` method only processes extractvalue instructions when the operand is not a call to a trivially   │
│ scalarizable intrinsic. This is because such calls should be handled by the `splitCall` function instead.                                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ Let me implement this fix:                                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                               │
│ # In visitExtractValueInst, return false for call instructions                                                                                                                        │
│ sed -i '1081a\    // Calls to trivially scalarizable intrinsics should be handled by splitCall,\n    // not by extractvalue scalarization.\n    return false;'                        │
│ ./llvm/lib/Transforms/Scalar/Scalarizer.cpp                                                                                                                                           │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                   │
